## Sprint progress
- Sprint 1 (Foundation rebuild): COMPLETE
  - Refactored `src/cli.js` into modules under `src/`.
  - Added dependencies: `cheerio`, `openai`, `@anthropic-ai/sdk`.
  - Added structured proof-point fields and expanded profile preferences.
  - Added REST API scaffold with local CRUD-style routes for core entities.
  - Added local API write protections and sql.js reload-on-request protection.
  - README updated for modular architecture and local-first REST examples.
- Sprint 2 (LLM scoring + tailoring): COMPLETE
  - Implemented provider-backed `src/llm.js.generateJson`.
  - Supported `JOBOS_LLM_PROVIDER`, `JOBOS_LLM_MODEL`, `JOBOS_LLM_API_KEY`, optional `JOBOS_LLM_BASE_URL` for OpenAI-compatible, Ollama Cloud, and Anthropic flows.
  - Replaced scoring/tailoring with provider-backed paths when configured and deterministic degraded-mode fallbacks when not.
  - Tailoring validates LLM proof mappings against stored proof point IDs and refuses unsupported mappings.
  - Added scoring eval fixtures and Sprint 2 tests.
- Sprint 3 (Research + outreach): COMPLETE
  - Implemented web-search-backed company dossier creation with source-backed facts and citations.
  - Implemented stakeholder discovery from public search results with affiliation filtering.
  - Implemented proof/company/stakeholder-aware outreach drafts that are draft-only and never sent.
  - Added Sprint 3 tests with a fake search server and outreach safety checks.
- Sprint 4 (Interview prep + analytics + dashboard + MCP): COMPLETE
  - Added `src/interview.js` and CLI command `jobos interview prep --application <id> --stage <stage>`.
  - Interview prep packets include role-specific likely questions, proof-linked STAR story prompts, interviewer questions, company/role refresh, warnings, and a human gate. LLM path validates proof IDs and renders stored proof summaries/metrics rather than freeform accomplishment details.
  - Rebuilt `src/analytics.js` with `analytics funnel --profile <id> --since <days>`, conversion metrics, grouping by source/stage/role family, and weekly review insights.
  - Upgraded `src/web.js` dashboard from read-only to interactive: kanban board, job/application/proof/task create/edit forms, artifact approve/reject UI, and local API wiring.
  - Extended `src/api.js` with dashboard/API job create/edit and artifact review endpoints; preserves internal `jobos:text:` URLs on manual-job round trips.
  - Added `src/mcp.js` stdio JSON-RPC/MCP server and `jobos mcp`, exposing: score_job, tailor_resume, draft_cover_letter, research_company, draft_outreach, create_application, update_application_status, list_tasks, interview_prep, weekly_review.
  - Added `tests/sprint4-interview-analytics-mcp.test.js` covering interview prep, analytics, dashboard/API approval and job creation, MCP tool list/framing, Unicode framing, and manual URL preservation.
  - Extended smoke to cover profile → import → score → tailor → track → interview prep → analytics → dashboard.
- Sprint 5 (Integration + polish + eval): NOT STARTED — NEXT

